data.description: MOVE-IN READY AND UPDATED NICELY! This South Lake Charles property offers 3 spacious bedrooms/2 full bathrooms, open concept kitchen/dining, hard surface flooring throughout, granite countertops and beautiful tile backsplash in the kitchen, upgraded tile in the main bathroom and much more. Step out into the rear yard and find a concrete patio and fully fenced yard for privacy. Over 1/3 acre lot located in flood zone X where flood insurance is not typically required by lenders. DON’T MISS THIS ONE – CALL TODAY!
